This is from the first 40 seconds of my session.  These files are  really 
good, probably some of my best so far.  This is using my raw audio  sound 
method, instead of using radio words.

I believe with this method, we can use anything to produce the  sounds.  
Although the sweep is almost maxed out for speed, the voices are  still clear 
and interactive regardless.

In one of the files, i&#39;m conversing with a spirit.  The skeptics can&#39;t  
possibly say this is just radio, with this method i finally have a leg to stand 
 on.

-Steve



